column2: SELECT TOP #      p.objid, s.specobjid, s.bestobjid, s.mjd, s.plate, s.fiberID,  p.ra, p.dec, s.z, s.scienceprimary, s.primTarget   , p.petromag_u, p.petromag_g, p.petromag_r, p.petromag_i, p.petromag_z into mydb.MyTable from photoobjall as p      JOIN specobjall  as s   ON p.objid = s.bestobjid
